in the paper every day.

47:07.033 --> 47:08.618
The secular press hates us

47:08.701 --> 47:11.621
because we're winning
millions of souls for Jesus.

47:12.664 --> 47:14.040
Oh, Tammy Faye.

47:14.207 --> 47:15.792
You follow blindly.

