49:47.026 --> 49:49.278
-

49:52.740 --> 49:54.826
-Can you...
-

49:54.909 --> 49:56.327
Can you talk to God?

49:57.995 --> 50:00.039
-I'm so tired and...
-

50:02.667 --> 50:03.668
Yes?

50:04.919 --> 50:06.254
I'll call you right back.

50:07.672 --> 50:08.756
I'll take it downstairs.

50:21.227 --> 50:22.478
Don't give up

50:23.020 --> 50:25.314
You're on the brink

50:25.481 --> 50:29.485
Of a miracle

50:29.652 --> 50:31.654
Don't give up

50:31.821 --> 50:36.200
Remember you're not alone

50:37.702 --> 50:42.081
People, don't give up
You're on the brink

50:42.248 --> 50:45.626
Of a miracle

50:45.793 --> 50:49.797
Don't give up on the brink

50:49.964 --> 50:54.010
-Of a miracle
-

50:54.177 --> 50:56.137
Don't give in

50:56.304 --> 50:59.974
God is still on the throne

51:00.183 --> 51:02.226
He's on His throne

51:02.643 --> 51:04.687
-Don't give up
-

51:04.854 --> 51:06.647
You nailed it.

51:06.814 --> 51:08.024
Really?

51:08.649 --> 51:11.235
This is sublime.
This is top drawer.

51:12.195 --> 51:13.696
You really think so, Gary?

51:14.322 --> 51:15.406
I know so.

51:15.573 --> 51:17.283
Your opinion means so much to me.

51:17.450 --> 51:19.243
I haven't been this excited
about working with an artist

51:19.410 --> 51:20.953
since I produced Monster Mash.

51:21.871 --> 51:24.373
That's really sweet.

51:24.916 --> 51:26.626
We could get a Grammy.

51:26.959 --> 51:28.920
-Really?
-Really.

51:34.967 --> 51:37.011
Tammy, it's time to go.
Time for the shoot.

51:37.136 --> 51:38.387
Come on. We're...

51:39.347 --> 51:40.681
Can you hear me?
Can you hear me?

51:40.765 --> 51:41.808
-Yeah.
