51:41.891 --> 51:44.227
so, let's go.
We're live in 15 minutes.

51:44.435 --> 51:46.062
Hey, hey, Jim, how are ya?

51:46.854 --> 51:48.314
Blessed, Gary, blessed.

51:48.397 --> 51:50.733
