She sings like an angel.

52:02.537 --> 52:05.331
Well, I'm never giving you
back to Nashville, oh, no!

52:06.249 --> 52:08.209
It's such a beautiful way
to connect, Jim.

52:08.376 --> 52:10.169
It's God's voice through my voice.

52:10.336 --> 52:11.754
To the world's ears.

52:12.338 --> 52:13.631
The things you say, Gary.

52:14.757 --> 52:16.634
Tammy! You're not camera ready.

52:16.801 --> 52:18.636
