and it's a big day.

52:18.803 --> 52:21.305
We gotta do 400 K today.
Can we shake a leg, please?

52:21.472 --> 52:23.391
Thank you.
I'm sorry to drag her away, Gary.

52:25.977 --> 52:27.061
Shake a leg, please.

52:27.228 --> 52:28.354
Sure thing, Mister.

52:28.437 --> 52:29.647
Thank you.

52:29.814 --> 52:31.274
-GARY: Jim.
-Thank you, Gary.

52:32.149 --> 52:33.276
-Tam?
