53:22.033 --> 53:23.284
Oh, yeah, that's right, Jim.

53:23.367 --> 53:25.369
It's been going on a long time.

53:26.245 --> 53:29.123
We are being persecuted
by the secular press

53:29.290 --> 53:33.753
