delivering the word of God every day.

53:47.016 --> 53:50.061
So, now is the time
for our prayer warriors

53:50.227 --> 53:53.105
to rise up because we are in a war.

53:53.898 --> 53:58.194
You know, Tammy and I,
we just hate to do this,

54:00.071 --> 54:02.156
but if every person watching

54:02.239 --> 54:05.576
