54:06.452 --> 54:09.789
that way, we can save
the word of God.

54:09.956 --> 54:11.832
I'm talking about salvation.

54:11.999 --> 54:16.796
Yours, mine, PTL's, the entire world's.

54:16.963 --> 54:20.216
So, together, if we agree together,

54:20.383 --> 54:23.177
let's give the devil a black eye.

54:24.553 --> 54:27.056
Oh, the phones are ringing. Oh.

54:27.139 --> 54:30.393
-Praise Jesus and praise you!
-

54:30.559 --> 54:33.104
And God bless you!
God bless you!

54:33.187 --> 54:34.522
TAMMY: Hallelujah!

54:34.689 --> 54:38.025
