God loves you.

54:38.567 --> 54:41.904
-He really, really does.
-He really does.

54:45.449 --> 54:46.575
MAN: Cut! Very good, everyone.

54:46.659 --> 54:48.160
That was not bad. How was that?

54:48.327 --> 54:50.955
-How was it?
