54:51.038 --> 54:53.124
-We need to talk. Now.
-Jim, it was great.

54:53.290 --> 54:55.751
FLETCHER: We're still gonna
be over budget on that...

54:59.088 --> 55:01.966
TAMMY: I just want the sleeves
a little shorter.

55:02.174 --> 55:04.010
Everything's about proportion.

55:05.720 --> 55:08.305
Okay, you ready to see?
Close your eyes.

55:10.349 --> 55:12.810
-I love it, Mother.
-

55:13.310 --> 55:14.979
Oh, Sissy, you look so beautiful, baby.

55:15.146 --> 55:16.439
-Thank you.
-

55:16.605 --> 55:18.774
RACHEL: Golly Moses,
this thing weighs a ton.

55:19.483 --> 55:20.526
Oh, goodness.

55:20.609 --> 55:22.445
RACHEL: Why do you have to do
so much shopping, Tam?

55:22.570 --> 55:24.905
Well, I have to get my exercise somehow.

55:25.072 --> 55:28.284
