58:22.458 --> 58:24.710
-I got you now. I got you now.
-JIM: Wanda! Wanda!

58:24.793 --> 58:25.836
FLETCHER: Wanda, come here.

58:25.920 --> 58:27.171
Come here and powder his nose.

58:27.254 --> 58:28.464
JIM: No! No!
FLETCHER: "Wanda, help.

58:28.547 --> 58:30.299
-"Wanda. Wanda.
-

