Somebody touched me

58:56.367 --> 58:57.701
Hallelujah

58:57.868 --> 59:01.538
Somebody touched me

59:02.039 --> 59:06.460
Oh, I was blind
But praise His name

59:06.627 --> 59:09.171
I now can see

59:10.965 --> 59:15.052
I was in darkness

59:15.219 --> 59:19.348
When Jesus found me

59:19.515 --> 59:23.394
But since He touched me

59:25.604 --> 59:31.402
I now am free

59:32.528 --> 59:33.612
-Wow.

59:33.696 --> 59:35.489
That was beautiful.
That was lovely, Tam.

59:35.656 --> 59:36.949
Gary.

59:38.450 --> 59:40.244
Aren't you glad He touched you?

59:40.411 --> 59:42.121
Truly. Yeah.

59:45.958 --> 59:48.002
Well, this is perfect. I love this.

59:48.168 --> 59:50.087
Well, it's all you,
Tam, it's all you.

59:50.254 --> 59:54.508
Oh, no. No, no.
You know I couldn't do this without you.

59:54.675 --> 59:58.220
You know, your voice
makes me feel closer to Him.

59:58.971 --> 1:00:00.973
Like He's right here.

1:00:02.766 --> 1:00:03.934
He is.

1:00:09.106 --> 1:00:13.319
when was the last time
that you were touched

1:00:15.029 --> 1:00:17.573
