how talented you are?

1:00:33.630 --> 1:00:34.631
Gary.

1:00:34.840 --> 1:00:37.634
Do his eyes tell you
how beautiful you are?

1:00:40.971 --> 1:00:43.390
Does he listen to you?

1:00:43.557 --> 1:00:45.559
Does he hear how amazing you are?

1:00:46.602 --> 1:00:47.811
Tammy.

1:00:47.978 --> 1:00:49.271
Yes.

1:00:49.855 --> 1:00:51.899
